<p>Sri Chaitanya Mahaprabhu is none other than the Supreme Lord Sri Krishna, who appeared in this Kali-yuga to inaugurate the yuga dharma for this age – Sankirtana, the congregational chanting of the Holy Names of the Lord.<br />
<a href="http://srikrishnamandir.org/philosophy/our-sampradaya/lord-caitanya-mahaprabhu/">Read More</a><br /></div></div><div class='clear_column'></div><br /></div></div>
